{"tid":2153125,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"PTU染疫 基地教官照除罩  議員斥警知法犯法 恐社區播毒","createTime":"2020-08-12T10:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T11:48:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"aa27f48c1939912584e19bd78607bf7166345b25","tid":2153125,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/PN43VT5W6TE7QVSQKNZLXHR4CA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FPN43VT5W6TE7QVSQKNZLXHR4CA%2F&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7akErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=6b161140\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FPN43VT5W6TE7QVSQKNZLXHR4CA%2F&h=f77d1589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/PN43VT5W6TE7QVSQKNZLXHR4CA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPTU染疫 基地教官照除罩 <br />\n議員斥警知法犯法 恐社區播毒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/D6PQtJcw962iBbFBqDHS-KkpD40=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/22UGZ565WNQEWNG7NLCMFWW6SE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FD6PQtJcw962iBbFBqDHS-KkpD40%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F22UGZ565WNQEWNG7NLCMFWW6SE.jpg&h=fa146ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粉嶺機動部隊訓練總部一名教官被拍到在集訓期間沒戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【武肺再爆發】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名駐守機動部隊（PTU）的23歲男警早前初步確診，惟有傳媒拍到在男警受訓的粉嶺機動部隊訓練總部，有教官漠視法令未有佩戴口罩，期間更與多名同袍交談。立法會議員斥警隊知法犯法，憂慮該教官一旦染疫將危及家人或警隊。<br />\n<br />\n涉事男警員周日初步確診武肺，但事隔兩日，尚未正式確診。衞生防護中心。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n初步確診兩日無更新<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：再增四死 累計奪59命<br />\n<br />\n根據警方早前公佈，男警本月8日自行前往指定診所檢測，翌日初步確診，染疫前在粉嶺蝴蝶山的訓練基地受訓。警方未有交代。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n翻查條例，若市民受僱工作期間正進行某活動，而該活動合理地需要不佩戴。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員郭家麒直斥教官離譜，指集訓是高危活動，大量流汗容易沾濕。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n連同23歲PTU男警，至今有八名警員染疫。2月一名防暴警病發後曾出席有60名。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"cd729b44911ce4950c76b140082deb9bbe55f9d7","tid":2153125,"uid":276440,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:58:23.000Z","msg":"每日都知法犯法"},{"pid":"1e15bce4e455f9ba5d08e0abfd1f115974e9c74a","tid":2153125,"uid":308567,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:59:14.000Z","msg":"是鳩但 你班柒頭係入面一鑊熟啦 我就帶撚住口罩係醫院門口開香檳"},{"pid":"83d682ff60fe4515b89c34df187543fcd260f259","tid":2153125,"uid":271516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:59:55.000Z","msg":"著住套衫係大曬"},{"pid":"af6e42313117dc228d8910bea1d675f23155a2a6","tid":2153125,"uid":296677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:00:28.000Z","msg":"唔除罩點3萬thx"},{"pid":"a86482e19c2beba4e35420f425fb99d4dc28237f","tid":2153125,"uid":154373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e15bce4e455f9ba5d08e0abfd1f115974e9c74a","tid":2153125,"uid":308567,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:59:14.000Z","msg":"是鳩但 你班柒頭係入面一鑊熟啦 我就帶撚住口罩係醫院門口開香檳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:01:06.000Z","msg":"真。戴到入官材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13620f1b51353637ad01e58171aa9f7798dc541a","tid":2153125,"uid":48161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:04:21.000Z","msg":"捽甩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b3c4f2008f129445cb8df6e3e473a46396d10b","tid":2153125,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:08:45.000Z","msg":"右邊個雄禿sir條頭毛好跳脫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a12730e94ed82a0a95b602319508df77bea3a4","tid":2153125,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:15:33.000Z","msg":"做運動點戴 唔